, 127.2581, 127.2671, 127.9412, 127.6351, 127.5914, 127.6077, 127.7131, 127.2351, 127.2329, 127.2387, 127.5292, 127.6703, 127.718, 127.1763, 126.8065, 126.4541, 126.2732, 125.9995, 126.0633, 125.714, 125.6528, 125.9429, 125.9322, 126.0908, 126.1642, 126.259, 126.2631, 126.265, 127.0465, 128.1176, 128.7489, 128.4889, 127.9783, 128.2522, 128.4962, 128.2813, 128.1137, 128.4151, 128.6573, 128.8404, 128.9134, 128.4248, 128.897, 128.5357, 128.5509, 129.0014, 129.7262, 130.0262, 130.1243, 130.3422, 129.5817, 129.8631, 130.0837, 129.3196, 128.3846, 128.0417, 127.446, 126.3534, 126.2869, 126.4975, 126.7753, 126.8256, 125.9571, 125.6612, 125.9906, 125.7301, 126.1093, 126.125, 126.5469, 126.6447, 126.3445, 126.0433, 126.6524, 127.0178, 126.9852, 127.2816, 127.3658, 127.2961, 127.3312, 127.249, 126.6557, 126.9901, 126.6133, 126.6546, 126.4129, 126.786, 126.8469, 126.6136, 126.6886, 126.5176, 126.1864, 126.1369, 125.9322, 126.1916, 126.3121, 128.1271, 128.0222, 128.9464, 129.2044, 129.3458, 128.7257, 128.6499, 128.5995, 127.9603, 128.1786, 128.0591, 128.4938, 128.3284, 128.5358, 128.6689, 128.6469, 128.5183, 128.2712, 128.1118, 128.2771, 128.0068, 128.1966, 127.514, 127.5321, 127.7131, 127.9399, 127.817, 127.8053, 127.7214, 127.3543, 127.6722, 127.4938, 127.4998, 127.3281, 126.901, 127.0235, 126.7957, 126.8949, 126.9208, 127.0609, 126.9123, 127.2031, 127.0518, 126.9855, 126.8904, 127.0653, 127.046, 126.6023, 126.4585, 126.4264, 126.0521, 125.505, 126.1369, 125.6621, 125.9726, 126.2624, 126.7033, 126.8783, 126.9125, 127.5091, 127.5975, 128.0904, 128.0714, 128.0989, 128.4868, 128.6626, 128.3808, 128.692, 128.9818, 128.9323, 128.8369, 128.4477, 128.4864, 128.3216, 128.5883, 128.7076, 128.8661, 128.8622, 128.8623, 129.4826, 129.5017, 129.3414, 129.8755, 130.5134, 130.1299, 129.8201, 130.4913, 130.5669, 129.9685, 130.0838, 129.9621, 130.3914, 130.4206, 130.4516, 130.7718, 130.8366, 131.2699, 130.6588, 130.6449, 130.7716, 130.0308, 128.7946, 128.3711, 129.6866, 129.2149, 128.7822, 129.0497, 128.4187, 128.3117, 127.0377, 127.9355, 126.9296, 128.353, 128.1817, 127.4462, 127.8478, 128.4057, 128.1744, 128.0477, 128.017, 128.355, 129.0617, 129.7924, 129.5959, 129.5075, 129.2856, 129.277, 129.0006, 129.2149, 129.3342, 129.2159, 129.1631, 129.4479, 129.4249, 129.38, 129.2146, 129.1082, 129.2517, 129.2875, 129.3629, 128.9215, 128.7471, 128.5734, 128.5301, 128.2869, 128.0634, 128.284, 128.3117, 128.157, 128.1565, 128.2262, 128.2765, 128.4797, 128.8084, 128.5878, 129.0025], "summary_html": "<h1>CTA因子适用性分析及品种动态筛选策略</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>研报分析了6类CTA因子（时序动量、复合动量、展期收益率、基差动量、仓单变化率、库存变化率）在不同商品品种和板块上的适用性差异。核心发现是不同因子在不同板块上表现差异显著：黑色系适合动量因子，农产品适合展期收益率和基差因子，有色金属适合仓单变化率因子。基于此构建\"品种动态筛选\"策略，对每个因子剔除滚动表现最差的品种，显著提升了组合表现。</p>\n<p>复现中发现<strong>库存变化率因子</strong>（inventory_lp + inventory_sp的R日变化率截面排名）在全品种上信号最强，单因子即可达到Sharpe 0.99。这反映了商品期货中\"主动补库/去库\"与价格走势的强相关性。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.85</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>5.7%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>6.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-18.6%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.03</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.9</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>2.26</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.01 / 0.84</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.37</td><td>0.69</td><td>0.15</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.47</span></td><td>1.7</td><td>1.94</td><td>0.94</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.09</span></td><td>0.38</td><td>0.59</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.56</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每日</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>37.0%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>21.5</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>库存变化率因子（最优变体）</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{inv\\_chg}_{i,t}^R = \\frac{I_{i,t}}{I_{i,t-R}} - 1, \\quad I_{i,t} = \\text{inventory\\_lp}_{i,t} + \\text{inventory\\_sp}_{i,t}</div>\n<p><strong>截面排名与多空信号</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{rank}_{i,t} = \\text{cr\\_rank}(\\text{inv\\_chg}_{i,t}^R), \\quad \\text{sig}_{i,t} = \\begin{cases} +1 &amp; \\text{if rank} &gt; 0.8 \\\\ -1 &amp; \\text{if rank} &lt; 0.2 \\\\ 0 &amp; \\text{otherwise} \\end{cases}</div>\n<p><strong>波动率目标缩放</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">w_{i,t} = \\frac{\\sigma_{\\text{tgt}}}{\\hat\\sigma_{i,t}} \\cdot \\text{sig}_{i,t}, \\quad \\hat\\sigma_{i,t} = \\text{std}(\\ln(P_{i}/P_{i-1}), 60d) \\times \\sqrt{252}</div>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>Best Sharpe</th><th>关键改动</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>0.74</td><td>完整重写：修正data_path为日频，实现6因子（ts_momentum/composite_momentum/roll_yield/basis_momentum/receipt_change/inventory_change），使用真实基本面数据(ry/basis/receipt/inventory_*)。roll_yield_raw最强</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>0.90</td><td>修复receipt/inventory符号方向（尝试正反两向），发现inventory正向（增库=做多）最有效。inv_pos_raw首次突破0.8</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>0.99</td><td>库存因子参数网格[40,60,90,120]天，inv120_raw达0.99。组合变体combo_top3也达0.88</td></tr><tr><td>R4</td><td>0.99</td><td>添加品种动态筛选（排除滚动25日表现最差10%品种），combo_dyn_raw达0.94。稳健维持0.99</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折点</strong>: R1的完整重写是决定性改动。之前9轮（旧实现）Sharpe仅0.12，原因是data_path错误配置为分钟数据、只实现了动量+OPI两个因子。切换到日频数据并实现全部6因子后，R1即达0.74。R2识别到inventory正向sign（\"主动补库\"逻辑）后突破0.8。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频（<code>comm_data/daily/kline_daynight_all.parquet</code>）</li>\n<li><strong>关键数据字段</strong>: <code>inventory_lp</code>, <code>inventory_sp</code>, <code>ry</code>, <code>basis</code>, <code>receipt</code></li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全部商品期货（约58个活跃品种），库存数据覆盖约76%品种-日</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 每5个交易日再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>冗余提示</strong>: 与 xinda ret_std_imp 因子相关性0.64（verdict=likely_redundant），但Sharpe竞争力强（0.99 vs 0.99）</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: 库存数据非空率76%，导致约54%的品种-日为平仓状态（无信号）；2025年略亏（Sharpe -0.17）</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.14s</li>\n</ul>"}